latestPosts.caption:
“The more complex and layered the character, the more creatively alive I feel.” – Priya Banerjee @priyabanerjee 

Our June Digital Cover Star @priyabanerjee opens up about her journey across multiple film industries, her love for staying in, and how she strikes a balance between fitness and food.

“I’m a complete homebody. Give me my dogs, home-cooked food, and a good movie—I’m happiest there,” she shares.

“I don’t follow diets. I love food too much, so I focus on moderation and balance instead.”

From her start in Telugu cinema to web series and now Bengali films, Priya’s career reflects her passion for versatility and depth in storytelling.

Read the full interview now at www.womenfitness.org

Photography: @pranav.foto 
Makeup: @makeupbychanch
